lead_paragraph: Detroit Tigers closer Francisco Rodriguez says he contracted the Zika virus over the offseason in his home country of Venezuela and advises potential Olympic athletes to educate themselves about the virus before heading to Rio de Janeiro.

headline.print_headline: Tigers Closer Rodriguez Says He Contracted Zika Virus
